RACE.RACE_TEXT: Middleburg Hunt Cup S. MIDDLEBURG RACE 3 3 1/4M Timber CR: N/A. Stakes Purse 25000. FOR FIVE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Five-yearolds, 165 lbs.; older, 170 lbs. Non-winners of two races over timber, allowed 5 lbs.; of a race, 10 lbs. (Apprentice rider timber races not considered).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: ANDI'AMU (FR) set pace jumping in tandem with STORM TEAM, went a length clear of that rival on the final circuit and prevailed driving when challenged by MYSTIC STRIKE. MYSTIC STRIKE staked the pacesetters two lengths back, rallied two fences out, dueled to wire but was outfinished. CRACKER FACTORY (GB) was unable to keep up with the top two pacesetters. STORM TEAM set the pace jumping in tandem with ANDI'AMU, gave way two fences out, dropped back and eased to the wire.
